annotationA: Intraflagellar transport 52; It is involved in the biological process described with: cilium morphogenesis; cilium assembly; microtubule-based movement
annotationB: Kinesin associated protein 3 (Kap3) is the non-motor accessory subunit of the heterotrimeric kinesin-2. Kap3 associates to the coiled-coil stalk domain of Klp68D andKlp64D. Kap3 plays an essential role in sensory cilia assembly and axonal transport
